posts.subject: Open letter asking for help......
posts.body:
A lot of creative effort went into these memes scraped from Donald.win. They deserve a wider audience than either Donald.win or 08chan can provide. But that will never happen unless clever LOCAL people find a way to make that happen, or some fearless fool  hosts these images on a clearweb site.

If that ever occurred, these memes would be emailed and texted everywhere. A virtuous cycle which is difficult to start and hard to stop.

So if you are a clever visitor....you could do what Zeronet can't. Put the work of these artists into the hands of people.....

Syncing here is not enough.
